{
  "stem": "1415.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, what happened is towards the end, I remember, and my friend told me that this man that came in, with a few others with him, was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I never remember seeing him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because like I say, I was so oblivious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had my own little world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my friend told me this was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were three of us from the same camp, and towards the end, we were all three together all the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We slept on the same bank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody told us if we can't sleep there or we can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't really have a head of the-- of the barracks, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- it was like, free-for-all type, except for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They still came in all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We still did not have any peace at all, ever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it seemed to have been a little more relaxed type.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember one time, they came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was towards the very end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was told this was Mengele that came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he tried to make us relax.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked us to please form like a circle around him, all around him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the kids just went around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stood around there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't dare to disobey a German ever, ever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stood around there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's telling us that-- I don't remember whether he told us that we are good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are good, and we are this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he tried to sort of butter us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he said, I know that a lot-- all of you have-- have family that are not with you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you want to be reunited with your family, we can do it for you.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
